{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:16:58.924867+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here is the complete list of CIFAR-10 models implemented in this repository, with their reported accuracy from the README.\n\n| Model | Reported Accuracy |\n|---|---|\n| VGG16 | 92.64% |\n| ResNet18 | 93.02% |\n| ResNet50 | 93.62% |\n| ResNet101 | 93.75% |\n| RegNetX_200MF | 94.24% |\n| RegNetY_400MF | 94.29% |\n| MobileNetV2 | 94.43% |\n| ResNeXt29(32x4d) | 94.73% |\n| ResNeXt29(2x64d) | 94.82% |\n| SimpleDLA | 94.89% |\n| DenseNet121 | 95.04% |\n| PreActResNet18 | 95.11% |\n| DPN92 | 95.16% |\n| DLA | 95.47% |\n| LeNet | *Not reported in README* |\n| SENet | *Not reported in README* |\n| PNASNet | *Not reported in README* |\n| GoogLeNet | *Not reported in README* |\n| ShuffleNet | *Not reported in README* |\n| ShuffleNetV2 | *Not reported in README* |\n| MobileNet (V1) | *Not reported in README* |\n| EfficientNet | *Not reported in README* |\n\n**Notes:**\n\n- All 22 model architectures are implemented as standalone Python files under `models/` and exported via `models/__init__.py`.\n- The first 14 models have reported accuracy figures in the README (ranging from 92.64% for VGG16 to 95.47% for DLA). The remaining 8 models (LeNet, SENet, PNASNet, GoogLeNet, ShuffleNet, ShuffleNetV2, MobileNetV1, EfficientNet) exist in the codebase but are not listed in the README accuracy table.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 932, "prompt_tokens": 7376, "total_tokens": 8308, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 490, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 7168}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 7168, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 208}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-flash", "system_fingerprint": "fp_8b330d02d0_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "65d8474